            <abstract>
                <p>A compilatory work of hagiographical notices and biblical excerpts, arranged in commemorations according to the days of the year as the synaxarion. It contains
                    commemorations that seem to be based upon those of <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4033Senkessar"/>, others that are very close
                    to those not present in the first recension, but added in <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4035SenkessarDL"/>,
                    and yet others that probably have different sources.
                    The work is attested in <ref type="mss" corresp="DW03"/>, where <persName ref="PRS13864GabraM"/> is named as its compiler. 
                    Two commemorations edited in <bibl><ptr target="bm:Sapeto1857Viaggio"/><citedRange unit="page">425-426; 437-438</citedRange></bibl>
                    from a "Senkessar di Bizan" attest the same text as the respective commemorations in <ref type="mss" corresp="DW03"/>.</p>
            </abstract>
